Franklin Ritchie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Franklin_Ritchie 0 Franklin Ritchie (June 26, 1865 – January 26, 1918) was an American actor of the silent film era. He appeared in 51 films between 1913 and 1917. He was born in Ritchie, Pennsylvania and died in Los Angeles, California.
